    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_gt.00008_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden<ptr target="loc.04256_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1882-06-22" rend="right">June 22 <choice>
                        <orig>Evn'g</orig>
                        <reg>Evening</reg>
                    </choice></date>
                </dateline>
               
                <salute>Dear young friend</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Yours <choice>
                <orig>rec'd</orig>
                <reg>received</reg>
            </choice> to-day, &#38; glad to hear from you&#8212;I have wanted to come down for
                quite a while, but business has delayed me. I am pretty well&#8212;&#38; all goes
                well enough to be thankful for in my affairs.&#8212;Only a short word this time but I will
                be down soon &#38; tell you all the news<ptr target="loc.04256_n2"/>&#8212;After I
                write this I am going out on the river for an hour or two&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">W W</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_gt.00007_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
